  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "There seems to be an issue with the L1 Block Number field that is present in the transaction for the Optimism block 15,000,000. The L1 Block Number that is returned by numerous node providers (Alchemy, Figment, QuickNode, etc.) for this block is 15,173,152. But according to https://optimistic.etherscan.io/tx/15000000, the L1 transaction that this Optimism block belongs to is located on Ethereum block 15,173,223.\r\n",
